# Project Structure Rules

## Folder Hierarchy

Every project MUST follow this numbered folder structure:

```
Projects/
  {{Project-Name}}/
    {{Project-Name}} MOC.md     # Required: Central hub
    
    00_Status & Roadmap/        # Dashboards, roadmaps, ADRs
    01_Market Analysis/         # TAM/SAM, competitors, SWOT
    02_User Research/           # Personas, empathy maps
    03_Product/                 # PRD, business canvases
    04_Design/                  # UX flows, wireframes
    05_Technical/               # Tech stack, architecture
    06_Engineering/             # Backlog, sprints
      Sprints/                  # Sprint notes subfolder
    07_Analytics & Growth/      # KPIs, experiments
    08_Legal & Privacy/         # GDPR, privacy
    09_Assets/                  # Images, files
    Archive/                    # Deprecated notes
```

## Creating a New Project

1. Create project folder in `Projects/`
2. Create all numbered subfolders (00-09 + Archive)
3. Create `{{Project-Name}} MOC.md` using `00_Project MOC.md` template
4. Create minimum viable docs:
   - `00_Status & Roadmap/Status_Dashboard.md`
   - `01_Market Analysis/Market_Overview.md`
   - `02_User Research/Persona_Primary.md`
   - `03_Product/Lean_Canvas.md`

